    <rigor-reason>Validation contract is canonical — all canonical error codes (10) must be implemented correctly; consumer code (wrappers, wizard steps, future surfaces) depends on the typed contract; NFR-09 a11y (live region) is load-bearing for screen-reader users. FULL guards against contract drift.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Aggregates validation from all 5 sub-components (012-018) into a single contract; must be implemented after sub-components land; downstream tasks (024-028) consume the contract.</parallel-reason>
